[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_dwarf_1_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Bloody seck. I thought we had seen everything this swamp has to offer. I should not have said that aloud, that just seems to be bringing the bad luck. How did you even make it here, anyway? The goddamn lithids sealed the cave entry behind. In return, we sealed their caves once we escaped. Ha!";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_dwarf_1_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "The seck, the goddamn seck! I hope some of my kin did not mine too deep again.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_man_1_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "It makes me sad to see the centaurs like this. They are said to have been magnificent creatures once. I was secretly hoping they still live somewhere in this swamp and might come to our rescue. No offense though, I still have faith in your and Adoniah's party.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_man_1_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "I liked the undead more when they sloppily walked. These undead gallop towards us at full speed. I wonder how much worse can the undead be?";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_man_2_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Ancient spirits born of fire are attacking ragged refugees withing this necromancy stronghold of a swamp. What threat could we pose to them?";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_man_2_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "The fact that we survived the seck assault is the only thing that gives me hope. There's no greater danger in this world, and we survived. I know now that we'll make it home safely.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_man_3_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "After my attempts to help with a bow almost got Croigord killed, I was politely asked to practice some more.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_man_3_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Perhaps Lizzith could cast a spell on me to increase my accuracy? I don't want to exhaust her though, as she's still shielding us from evil magical entities.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_man_4_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "These red swamp flowers have an interesting bittersweet taste. I'm collecting them so that I can flavor my beer with them. I'm sure our adventurous friends have never tasted anything like that.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_man_4_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "I'm actually worried that beer will taste great with these flowers. What will I do when I run out of them?";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_man_big_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Nothing really ever prepares you for facing a flock of seck.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_man_big_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Seck assassinating a group of villagers in the darkest of swamps. Now we have our own fantastic story to tell by the fires.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_woman_1_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Hey, you're alive! How fortunate! Look, I already learnt to summon a desert braak. I'll never be a mystic like Lizzith, but I'm becoming a proficient combat mage.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_woman_1_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "I'm practicing pillar of fire, but I've had not luck casting it so far.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_woman_2_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Seeing a few people smash thousands of monster into pieces makes me think. Can you imagine how powerful could we as a race become if each of us learnt how to fight? We'd have no enemy to be afraid of.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_refugee_woman_2_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "I'm feeling ashamed about how delicate I have become in my life. I should be holding a sword by Tristeth's and Addires's side.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_party_droog_1_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Another day, another fresh horror cast upon us. My hands are getting sore from holding this mace.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_party_droog_1_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "My fighting days will be over once we leave civilisation. I'll probably become a messanger or a scholar. Neither of them requires a pair of healthy hands.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_party_droog_2_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Finally, enemies with decent weapons and armor. I'm beginning to think this journey might no leave us financially in ruin.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_party_droog_2_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Our supplies are dwindling. We need someplace to restock soon, or we'll fall to our enemies due to exhaustion.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_party_goblin_1_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		choice = shop;
		screen_text = "Hello friend. Many did not expect to see you again after the lithids sealed us in the caves. Hope you've had a pleasant journey. Ha-ha-ha-ha-ha. Nothing? Nevermind. Would you like to see what I managed to collect along the way?";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_party_goblin_1_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		choice = shop;
		screen_text = "What can I brighten your day with?";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_party_leader_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		activate_quest* = lyottia_quest_20_safe_passage,0;
		activate_quest* = lyottia_quest_20_seck,0;
		screen_text = "My treasured friend, how could you have made it here? When Lizzith sensed your victory, we moved on through the caverns. Lithids were quick to seal the entrance after us. They pounced upon us with every step we took. Once we finally made it out, we sealed the cave exit behind us - for good reasons, believe me. You know the rest, you arrived just in time to see those seck attack. I had not known they still existed. And how was your passage? Ah, you believed we had risen as undead? That must have put you into dark place. I suspect the seck were involved in that, too. They are known to be master tricksters. Now, shall we return to the old operative mode? There's a mighty lich residing in cliffs above our position. Take care of him, and we'll move out again.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_party_leader_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "That seck menace has me worried. They don't just attack passersby for no reason. We'll need to investigate this further once we're out.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_party_man_2_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "I never expected to face seck in battle. I must say, even with all the fighting experience I have, I'm still tembling. These matters are getting serious.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_party_man_2_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "I hope there won't be any more seck ambushes. We can take down thousands of undead monsters, but these seck are something different.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_party_woman_1_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "This is Adoniah's fault. Our camp should have been more wary. Those seck nearly bested us. If it was up to me, all the civilians would be throwing spears at enemies all the time.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_party_woman_1_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "I swear, the next time someone wanders away from the camp, I'm cutting their head off.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_party_woman_2_first]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "The seck attack is troubling, but we have more pressing matter. There's a powerful lich in the cliffs above us. I don't want him attacking us from the rear. Will you take care of him? That would let us move on.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}
[lyottia_conversation_20_party_woman_2_next]
{
	[text*]
	{
		screen_text = "Destroy the lich in the cliffs above, and we'll be able to move on.";
	  f scroll_rate = 10.000000;
	}
}